description:
This feature includes registering, Modifying and Approval of Business Admin and
    Customer Support Admin Users by System Admin
name: User Management : Subscriber

elements.name: To verify that valid SystemAdmin/businsess User is able to initiate Subscriber creation for suspension and Resumption

Navigate to User Management and Click on register
Select User type as Subscriber and click on Subscriber

User click on submitted user data
Approve the Users
